sections.Trivia:
- The suspects' names are related to "barbecue"[2] :
Takushi Kon'no (紺野 宅司) comes from gas burners (コンロ ,konro?) and skewers (串 ,kushi?) ;
Sumika Kon'no (紺野 純夏) comes from gas burners (コンロ ,konro?) and charcoal (炭 ,sumi?).
